{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs","slug":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs","title":"The Island of Forgotten Songs","title_ko":"잊힌 노래의 섬","level":"B1","ageBand":"11-13","coverUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/cover.webp","summary_ko":"사람들이 잊은 옛 노래들이 모여 사는 섬을 찾아가 한 곡을 배워 마을로 돌려보내는 따뜻한 이야기예요.","wordCount":287,"pages":[{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"Mara and Theo lived in a quiet village by the sea.","translation_ko":"마라와 테오는 바닷가의 조용한 마을에 살았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Mara","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":460},{"word":"and","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":460,"endMs":760},{"word":"Theo","charStart":9,"charEnd":13,"startMs":760,"endMs":1080},{"word":"lived","charStart":14,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1440},{"word":"in","charStart":20,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1580},{"word":"a","charStart":23,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1580,"endMs":1760},{"word":"quiet","charStart":25,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1760,"endMs":2100},{"word":"village","charStart":31,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2100,"endMs":2460},{"word":"by","charStart":39,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2460,"endMs":2720},{"word":"the","charStart":42,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2720,"endMs":2960},{"word":"sea","charStart":46,"charEnd":49,"startMs":2960,"endMs":3140}]},{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"Every evening, an old fisherman told stories on the dock.","translation_ko":"저녁마다 늙은 어부가 부두에서 이야기를 들려주었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Every","charStart":0,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"evening","charStart":6,"charEnd":13,"startMs":380,"endMs":760},{"word":"an","charStart":15,"charEnd":17,"startMs":760,"endMs":1000},{"word":"old","charStart":18,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1320},{"word":"fisherman","charStart":22,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1320,"endMs":1640},{"word":"told","charStart":32,"charEnd":36,"startMs":1640,"endMs":2060},{"word":"stories","charStart":37,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2460},{"word":"on","charStart":45,"charEnd":47,"startMs":2460,"endMs":2660},{"word":"the","charStart":48,"charEnd":51,"startMs":2660,"endMs":2820},{"word":"dock","charStart":52,"charEnd":56,"startMs":2820,"endMs":3060}]}]},{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"One night he said, \"Far away, there is an island of forgotten songs.\"","translation_ko":"어느 밤 그가 말했어요. \"저 멀리 잊힌 노래의 섬이 있단다.\"","audioUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"One","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"night","charStart":4,"charEnd":9,"startMs":300,"endMs":560},{"word":"he","charStart":10,"charEnd":12,"startMs":620,"endMs":760},{"word":"said","charStart":13,"charEnd":17,"startMs":760,"endMs":1040},{"word":"Far","charStart":20,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1820},{"word":"away","charStart":24,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1820,"endMs":2120},{"word":"there","charStart":30,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2120,"endMs":2600},{"word":"is","charStart":36,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2600,"endMs":2740},{"word":"an","charStart":39,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2740,"endMs":3020},{"word":"island","charStart":42,"charEnd":48,"startMs":3020,"endMs":3200},{"word":"of","charStart":49,"charEnd":51,"startMs":3200,"endMs":3500},{"word":"forgotten","charStart":52,"charEnd":61,"startMs":3500,"endMs":3860},{"word":"songs","charStart":62,"charEnd":67,"startMs":3860,"endMs":4280}]},{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"When people stop singing a song, it drifts there to wait.\"","translation_ko":"\"사람들이 어떤 노래를 더는 부르지 않으면, 그 노래는 그곳으로 떠내려가 기다린단다.\"","audioUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"When","charStart":1,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":340},{"word":"people","charStart":6,"charEnd":12,"startMs":340,"endMs":860},{"word":"stop","charStart":13,"charEnd":17,"startMs":860,"endMs":1260},{"word":"singing","charStart":18,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1260,"endMs":1540},{"word":"a","charStart":26,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1540,"endMs":2060},{"word":"song","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2060},{"word":"it","charStart":34,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2520,"endMs":2760},{"word":"drifts","charStart":37,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2760,"endMs":2980},{"word":"there","charStart":44,"charEnd":49,"startMs":2980,"endMs":3260},{"word":"to","charStart":50,"charEnd":52,"startMs":3260,"endMs":3500},{"word":"wait","charStart":53,"charEnd":57,"startMs":3500,"endMs":3660}]}]},{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"Mara remembered a lullaby her grandmother used to sing.","translation_ko":"마라는 할머니가 불러 주시던 자장가를 떠올렸어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Mara","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":480},{"word":"remembered","charStart":5,"charEnd":15,"startMs":480,"endMs":920},{"word":"a","charStart":16,"charEnd":17,"startMs":920,"endMs":1200},{"word":"lullaby","charStart":18,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1580},{"word":"her","charStart":26,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1580,"endMs":1820},{"word":"grandmother","charStart":30,"charEnd":41,"startMs":1820,"endMs":2280},{"word":"used","charStart":42,"charEnd":46,"startMs":2280,"endMs":2580},{"word":"to","charStart":47,"charEnd":49,"startMs":2580,"endMs":2840},{"word":"sing","charStart":50,"charEnd":54,"startMs":2840,"endMs":3000}]},{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p3-s2","ord":1,"text":"She had tried for years, but she could not recall the tune.","translation_ko":"여러 해 동안 애썼지만, 그 가락이 도무지 기억나지 않았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/audio/p3-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"She","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"had","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":260,"endMs":460},{"word":"tried","charStart":8,"charEnd":13,"startMs":460,"endMs":700},{"word":"for","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":700,"endMs":960},{"word":"years","charStart":18,"charEnd":23,"startMs":960,"endMs":1320},{"word":"but","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1600,"endMs":1860},{"word":"she","charStart":29,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1860,"endMs":2060},{"word":"could","charStart":33,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2180},{"word":"not","charStart":39,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2180,"endMs":2420},{"word":"recall","charStart":43,"charEnd":49,"startMs":2420,"endMs":2740},{"word":"the","charStart":50,"charEnd":53,"startMs":2740,"endMs":3040},{"word":"tune","charStart":54,"charEnd":58,"startMs":3040,"endMs":3180}]}]},{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p4","pageNo":4,"spread":"p4","imageUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/p4.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"The next morning, the two friends pushed a small boat into the waves.","translation_ko":"다음 날 아침, 두 친구는 작은 배를 파도 속으로 밀어 넣었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/audio/p4-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":180},{"word":"next","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":180,"endMs":480},{"word":"morning","charStart":9,"charEnd":16,"startMs":480,"endMs":880},{"word":"the","charStart":18,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1180},{"word":"two","charStart":22,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1400},{"word":"friends","charStart":26,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1660},{"word":"pushed","charStart":34,"charEnd":40,"startMs":1660,"endMs":1960},{"word":"a","charStart":41,"charEnd":42,"startMs":1960,"endMs":2180},{"word":"small","charStart":43,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2180,"endMs":2460},{"word":"boat","charStart":49,"charEnd":53,"startMs":2460,"endMs":2640},{"word":"into","charStart":54,"charEnd":58,"startMs":2640,"endMs":2920},{"word":"the","charStart":59,"charEnd":62,"startMs":2920,"endMs":3100},{"word":"waves","charStart":63,"charEnd":68,"startMs":3100,"endMs":3360}]},{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p4-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"If the island is real, we will find it,\" Theo said.","translation_ko":"\"섬이 정말 있다면, 우리가 찾아낼 거야.\" 테오가 말했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/audio/p4-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"If","charStart":1,"charEnd":3,"startMs":30,"endMs":257},{"word":"the","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":257,"endMs":484},{"word":"island","charStart":8,"charEnd":14,"startMs":484,"endMs":879},{"word":"is","charStart":15,"charEnd":17,"startMs":879,"endMs":1106},{"word":"real","charStart":18,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1106,"endMs":1425},{"word":"we","charStart":24,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1425,"endMs":1652},{"word":"will","charStart":27,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1652,"endMs":1879},{"word":"find","charStart":32,"charEnd":36,"startMs":1879,"endMs":2106},{"word":"it","charStart":37,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2106,"endMs":2425},{"word":"Theo","charStart":42,"charEnd":46,"startMs":2425,"endMs":2652},{"word":"said","charStart":47,"charEnd":51,"startMs":2652,"endMs":3030}]}]},{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/p5.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p5-s1","ord":0,"text":"They rowed all day while the sun moved slowly across the sky.","translation_ko":"해가 하늘을 천천히 가로지르는 동안 둘은 온종일 노를 저었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/audio/p5-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"They","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":420},{"word":"rowed","charStart":5,"charEnd":10,"startMs":420,"endMs":780},{"word":"all","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":780,"endMs":1300},{"word":"day","charStart":15,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1640},{"word":"while","charStart":19,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1640,"endMs":2100},{"word":"the","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":2100,"endMs":2360},{"word":"sun","charStart":29,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2360,"endMs":2580},{"word":"moved","charStart":33,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2580,"endMs":2940},{"word":"slowly","charStart":39,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2940,"endMs":3460},{"word":"across","charStart":46,"charEnd":52,"startMs":3460,"endMs":3880},{"word":"the","charStart":53,"charEnd":56,"startMs":3880,"endMs":4220},{"word":"sky","charStart":57,"charEnd":60,"startMs":4220,"endMs":4460}]},{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p5-s2","ord":1,"text":"By evening, a thick gray mist wrapped around their boat.","translation_ko":"저녁이 되자 짙은 잿빛 안개가 배를 감쌌어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/audio/p5-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"By","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":280},{"word":"evening","charStart":3,"charEnd":10,"startMs":280,"endMs":840},{"word":"a","charStart":12,"charEnd":13,"startMs":1040,"endMs":1480},{"word":"thick","charStart":14,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1480,"endMs":1760},{"word":"gray","charStart":20,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1760,"endMs":2060},{"word":"mist","charStart":25,"charEnd":29,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2380},{"word":"wrapped","charStart":30,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2380,"endMs":2780},{"word":"around","charStart":38,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2780,"endMs":3140},{"word":"their","charStart":45,"charEnd":50,"startMs":3140,"endMs":3360},{"word":"boat","charStart":51,"charEnd":55,"startMs":3360,"endMs":3600}]}]},{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p6","pageNo":6,"spread":"p6","imageUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/p6.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p6-s1","ord":0,"text":"Inside the mist, the world grew silent and strange.","translation_ko":"안개 속에서 세상은 고요하고 낯설어졌어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/audio/p6-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Inside","charStart":0,"charEnd":6,"startMs":0,"endMs":420},{"word":"the","charStart":7,"charEnd":10,"startMs":420,"endMs":660},{"word":"mist","charStart":11,"charEnd":15,"startMs":660,"endMs":960},{"word":"the","charStart":17,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1540},{"word":"world","charStart":21,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1720},{"word":"grew","charStart":27,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1720,"endMs":2000},{"word":"silent","charStart":32,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2000,"endMs":2460},{"word":"and","charStart":39,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2460,"endMs":3100},{"word":"strange","charStart":43,"charEnd":50,"startMs":3100,"endMs":3500}]},{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p6-s2","ord":1,"text":"Then, very faintly, they heard humming on the wind.","translation_ko":"그때 아주 희미하게, 바람결에 흥얼거리는 소리가 들렸어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/audio/p6-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Then","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":400},{"word":"very","charStart":6,"charEnd":10,"startMs":600,"endMs":980},{"word":"faintly","charStart":11,"charEnd":18,"startMs":980,"endMs":1400},{"word":"they","charStart":20,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1720},{"word":"heard","charStart":25,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1720,"endMs":1900},{"word":"humming","charStart":31,"charEnd":38,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2220},{"word":"on","charStart":39,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2220,"endMs":2480},{"word":"the","charStart":42,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2480,"endMs":2600},{"word":"wind","charStart":46,"charEnd":50,"startMs":2600,"endMs":2800}]}]},{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p7","pageNo":7,"spread":"p7","imageUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/p7.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-island-of-forgotten-songs-p7-s1","ord":0,"text":"The boat touched soft sand, and the mist opened like a curtain.","translation_ko":"배가 부드러운 모래에 닿자, 안개가 커튼처럼 열렸어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-island-of-forgotten-songs/audio/p7-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":280},{"word":"boat","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":280,"endMs":600},{"word":"touched","charS